<h2 itemprop="name">
New commenting system on the Template Market </h2>
<dl class="article-info">
<dt class="article-info-term"></dt>
<dd class="createdby" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
<span itemprop="name" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Written by ">Paul Frankowski</span> </dd>
<dd class="category-name">
<i class="fa fa-folder-open-o"></i>
<a href="/blog" itemprop="genre" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Article Category">Blog</a> </dd>
<dd class="comment">
<i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>
<span class="comments-anchor">
<a href="https://shapebootstrap.net/blog/5-new-commenting-system-on-the-template-market#disqus_thread"></a>
</span>
</dd>
<dd class="create">
<i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>
<time datetime="2015-07-02T13:26:46+06:00" itemprop="dateCreated" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Created Date">
02 July 2015 </time>
</dd>
<dd class="hits">
<span class="fa fa-eye"></span>
<meta itemprop="interactionCount" content="UserPageVisits:1264"/>
Hits: 1264</dd>
</dl>
